.An Ingo Schwarze Aq Mt schwarze@openbsd.org
.Sh CAVEATS
The
.Nm
utility only partially validates the database format.
For complete validation, use the
.Xr dbm_dump 1
utility found in
.Pa /usr/src/regress/usr.bin/mandoc/db/dbm_dump/ .
